 Write a program to display only those records whose name
starts with "K" from the data file named "record.txt" which
contains Roll number, Name, Address, and Class of several Student.

OPEN "record.txt" FOR INPUT AS #1
CLS
DO WHILE NOT EOF(1)
    INPUT #1, r, n$, a$, c
    IF LEFT$(UCASE$(n$), 1) = "K" THEN
        PRINT r, n$, a$, c
    END IF
LOOP
CLOSE #1
END
        
